*[[克里斯·派恩|克里斯·派恩]]饰[[詹姆斯·T·柯克|詹姆斯·T·柯克]]。派恩认为他的第一次试演非常糟糕，因为他无法让自己严肃起来，从而无法令人觉得他是一名领袖。<ref name=new>{{cite news|author=Jeff Jensen|title='Star Trek': New Movie, New Vision|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|date=2008-10-24|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20233502,00.html|accessdate=2008-10-16|archive-date=2008-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081104040237/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20233502,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾布拉姆斯并没有观看派恩的第一次试演，当派恩的经纪人与艾布拉姆斯的妻子见面后，导演决定再给派恩一次机会，让他与昆图试演对手戏。昆图支持派恩出演这一角色，因为他们曾在一起工作，并得以相互了解。<ref name=boldrevisit>{{cite news|author=John Jurgensen|title=Boldly Revisiting Roles|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=2009-01-02|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB123084942774447411.html|accessdate=2009-01-16|archive-date=2009-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415205912/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB123084942774447411.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在得到这一角色后，派恩向[[威廉·夏特纳|威廉·夏特纳]]寄送了一封信件，夏特纳回信表示赞成他出演柯克。派恩观看了电视剧的经典情节，并阅读了有关《[[星际旅行|星际旅行]]》宇宙的百科全书，但却为自己必须复制夏特纳的角色一事感到忧郁。派恩觉得自己必须表现出柯克的“幽默、傲慢与果断”，但却不应表现出夏特纳说话的方式，否则便有模仿的嫌疑。<ref name=boldrevisit />派恩提到，当他观看初-{}-代电视剧时，他还被夏特纳表现幽默的方式所打动。<ref name=wondercon>{{cite news|title=Wondercon 09: Star Trek Panel Detailed Report & Pictures|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2009-02-28|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/28/wondercon-09-star-trek-panel-detailed-report-pictures/|accessdate=2009-03-01|archive-date=2009-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090302045330/http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/28/wondercon-09-star-trek-panel-detailed-report-pictures/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，派恩还打算在自己的角色中加入[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]在《壮志凌云》中与[[哈里森·福特|哈里森·福特]]饰演[[印第安那·琼斯|印第安那·琼斯]]与[[韩·索罗|韩·索罗]]时的一些元素。<ref>{{cite news|author=Sally Browne|title=Chris Pine fills big shoes in Star Trek's latest enterprise|work=The Courier-Mail|date=2009-04-19|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25346545-7642,00.html|accessdate=2009-04-18|archive-date=2009-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090421091728/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25346545-7642,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
**{{link-en|吉米·贝内特|Jimmy Bennett}}饰儿童时期的詹姆斯·柯克。
*[[扎克瑞·昆图|-{zh-cn:扎克瑞·昆图; zh-tw:柴克瑞·恩杜; zh-hk:沙查·昆圖;}-]]饰[[斯波克|斯波克]]。昆图对饰演斯波克很感兴趣，因为他着迷于斯波克半人类、半[[瓦肯|瓦肯人]]的二元性，<ref name=new />以及“他不懈追求的那些概念，如何在成长中负起责任，如何在成长中表现尊重。我认为这些是我们这个社会、乃至这个世界应该学习的。”<ref>原文：“he is constantly exploring that notion of how to evolve in a responsible way and how to evolve in a respectful way. I think those are all things that we as a society, and certainly the world, could implement.”</ref><ref name="grandspocks">{{cite news | author = Anthony Pascale | title = Grand Slam XVI: Two Spocks Rock The House | work = Trek Movie | date = 2008-04-14 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/04/14/grand-slam-xvi-two-spocks-rock-the-house/ | accessdate = 2008-04-15 | archive-date = 2008-04-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080416033131/http://trekmovie.com/2008/04/14/grand-slam-xvi-two-spocks-rock-the-house/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>他提到，在2006年12月接受《[[匹兹堡新闻邮报|匹兹堡新闻邮报]]》采访时，他了解到了这部新电影，并表达了出演的兴趣：采访的这篇文章后来被广泛地传播，并吸引了艾布拉姆斯的兴趣。<ref name=quintotrekmovie>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Interview with Zachary Quinto|work=TrekMovie|date=2009-05-05|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/05/05/exclusive-interview-with-zachary-quinto/|accessdate=2009-05-07|archive-date=2009-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090508122950/http://trekmovie.com/2009/05/05/exclusive-interview-with-zachary-quinto/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在试演时，昆图穿着一件蓝衬衣，并[[刘海_(发型)|把头发弄平]]，以让自己更像斯波克。<ref name=boldrevisit />为了演好这一角色，他把自己的手指绑在一起练习[[瓦肯举手礼|瓦肯举手礼]]，剃掉了自己的眉毛，甚至还蓄发、染发成斯波克的发型。<ref name=new />他还继承了斯波克的许多特点，譬如当其静立时，尼莫伊通常会把双手放在身后。<ref name=boldrevisit />昆图认为这些身体上的改变有助于饰演一名外星人，<ref name=new />还开玩笑说到：“我感觉自己就像一个书呆子。我觉得我又回到了12岁的时候。看看我过去的照片你就会看见我的{{link-en|瓜皮头|bowl cut}}。我天生就是演斯波克的料。因为这个样子，我至少要被嘲笑个四五年。”<ref>原文：“I just felt like a nerd. I felt like I was 12 again. You look back at those pictures and you see the bowl cut. There's no question I was born to play the Spock role. I was sporting that look for a good four or five years.”</ref><ref name=boldrevisit />在昆图得到这一角色前，导演还与[[阿德里安·布罗迪|阿德里安·布罗迪]]讨论过出演的事宜。<ref>{{cite news | author = Josh Horowitz | title = Adrien Brody Confirms He Was Almost Mr. Spock | work = [[MTV|MTV]] | date = 2007-09-26 | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/09/26/adrien-brody-confirms-he-was-almost-mr-spock/ | accessdate = 2007-10-06 | archive-date = 2015-10-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004101626/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/09/26/adrien-brody-confirms-he-was-almost-mr-spock/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>
**[[雅各布·科根|雅各布·科根]]饰儿童时期的斯波克。
**[[伦纳德·尼莫伊|伦纳德·尼莫伊]]再次出演了他的角色——来自未来的老年斯波克（在电影片尾字幕中写的是第一位斯波克{{small|（Spock Prime）}}）。在得到这一角色后，尼莫伊与昆图成为了好友。尽管昆图在拍摄的空档期间观看了部分电视剧，但尼莫伊才是他学习扮演斯波克的主要源泉。<ref name=wondercon />艾布拉姆斯与编剧曾前往尼莫伊的家中拜访他；编剧[[罗伯托·奥利奇|罗伯托·奥利奇]]回忆说，在他们告诉尼莫伊他将有多么重要前，尼莫伊表现出了一种“‘你们这些人到底是谁，到底想要做什么’的情绪”<ref>原文：“'Who are you guys and what are you up to?' vibe”．</ref>。尼莫伊表现得十分平静，而他的妻子苏珊·贝告诉创作小组说，在他们的谈话结束后，尼莫伊在椅子上长坐不起，为自己在多次谢绝后再次同意重演这一角色的决定感到不知所措。<ref name=cling>{{cite news|author=Geoff Boucher|title='Star Trek' writing pair cling on to their partnership|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|date=2009-03-29|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/mar/29/entertainment/ca-startrek29|accessdate=2009-03-29|archive-date=2009-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904052349/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/mar/29/entertainment/ca-startrek29|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于尼莫伊不喜欢原来的剧本，制片方不得不停下制片进度，对剧本重新进行改写。<ref name="grandslam" />剧本表现出的大尺度以及各角色的背景故事令尼莫伊感到“异常兴奋”，<ref>原文：“genuinely excited”．</ref><ref name="grandspocks" />他说：“我们已经表现过［斯波克半人类、半瓦肯人的特质］，但从来没有像这出剧本那样在角色的历史、成长、来历以及齐聚为进取号船员的角度上来探讨它。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Exclusive: A Conversation with Trek's Two Spocks |work=[[电视指南|电视指南]] |date=2008-04-15 |url=http://movies.tvguide.com/movie-news/Exclusive-Conversation-Treks-9524.aspx |accessdate=2008-04-15 |quote=We have dealt with [Spock being half-human, half-Vulcan], but never with quite the overview that this script has of the entire history of the character, the growth of the character, the beginnings of the character and the arrival of the character into the ''Enterprise'' crew. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081021105722/http://movies.tvguide.com/movie-news/Exclusive-Conversation-Treks-9524.aspx |archivedate=2008-10-21 }}</ref>艾布拉姆斯说：“执导他去饰演斯波克简直太不可思议了，因为我到底在做什么？这个人已经演了四十年的斯波克了。就像是‘我觉得斯波克应该……’”。<ref>{{cite news|title=Abrams and Orci On Fan Reaction + Bob Meets Brannon|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2009-01-16|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/01/16/abrams-and-orci-on-fan-reaction/|accessdate=2009-01-16|quote=it was surreal to direct him as Spock, because what the hell am I doing there? This guy has been doing it for forty years. It's like 'I think Spock would...'|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308084137/https://trekmovie.com/2009/01/16/abrams-and-orci-on-fan-reaction/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*[[卡尔·厄本|卡尔·厄本]]饰[[伦纳德·麦科伊|伦纳德·麦科伊医生（老骨头）]]。和派恩一样，厄本觉得饰演这一角色“不在于模仿和复制，而在于忠于并真实表现出当年{{link-en|德福雷斯特·凯利|DeForest Kelley}}所表现出的精髓，并要为角色带入一些新的元素”。<ref>原文：“it is a case of not doing some sort of facsimile or carbon copy, but really taking the very essence of what DeForest Kelley has done and honoring that and bringing something new to the table”．</ref>从7岁开始，厄本便成为了《星际旅行》的爱好者，在同儿子观看了系列的DVD版本后，他开始积极谋求出演这一角色。<ref>{{cite news | author = Eric Goldman | title = Karl Urban: From Comanche Moon to Star Trek | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2008-01-09 | url = http://uk.tv.ign.com/articles/844/844578p2.html | accessdate = 2008-01-23 | archive-date = 2008-03-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080314152826/http://uk.tv.ign.com/articles/844/844578p2.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>在同艾布拉姆斯首次见面的两个月后，厄本进行了他的第一次试演。他说，他乐于饰演这名喜剧色彩浓厚的角色，这是他在《{{link-en|牛奶的代价|The Price of Milk}}》后再也没有做过的事，因为他疲于饰演动作类的角色了。当被问及麦科伊的坏脾气时，厄本开玩笑说到，这个角色可能“的确有些[[躁郁症|躁郁]]”。<ref>{{cite news|title=Karl Urban on Star Trek and beyond|work=[[新西兰先驱报|新西兰先驱报]]|date=2009-04-09|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10565861&pnum=0|accessdate=2009-04-11|quote=little bipolar actually!|archive-date=2012-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121043156/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/entertainment/news/article.cfm?c_id=1501119&objectid=10565861&pnum=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>厄本曾与奥利奇与库兹曼在《[[齐娜武士公主|齐娜武士公主]]》中合作过，他在其中饰演[[丘比特|丘比特]]与{{link-en|凯撒 (齐娜)|Caesar (Xena)|凯撒}}。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://trekmovie.com/2007/09/28/karl-urban-up-for-star-trek-role-but-not-villain-casting-plot-updates/|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Karl Urban Up For ‘Star Trek’ Role (But Not Villain) + Casting & Plot Updates|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2007-09-28|accessdate=2008-12-28|archive-date=2008-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223194616/http://trekmovie.com/2007/09/28/karl-urban-up-for-star-trek-role-but-not-villain-casting-plot-updates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*[[佐伊·萨尔达尼亚|佐伊·萨尔达尼亚]]饰[[乌乎拉|妮欧塔·乌乎拉]]。艾布拉姆斯喜欢她的表演，并请求她出演这一角色。萨尔达尼亚从未看过原初电视剧，不过她曾在《[[航站情緣|航站情緣]]》（2004年）中扮演一名{{link-en|星迷|Trekkie}}，在艾布拉姆斯对她大加赞誉后，她答应出演这一角色。“对一名演员来说，这就是你所需要你想得到的。让你的同僚们认可并尊重你”，<ref>原文：“For an actor, that's all you need, that's all you want. To get the acknowledgment and respect from your peers”．</ref>她这样说道。她与[[尼切尔·尼科尔斯|尼切尔·尼科尔斯]]见了面，尼科尔斯向她介绍了乌乎拉的背景资料及其名字的来历。<ref>{{cite news | author = Wilson Morales | title = Zoe Saldaña sheds a little light on playing 'Uhura' | work = Blackfilm | date = 2008-01-29 | url = http://www.blackfilm.com/20080125/features/startrekupdate.shtml | accessdate = 2008-01-30 | archive-date = 2008-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080201090407/http://blackfilm.com/20080125/features/startrekupdate.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>萨尔达尼亚的母亲是一名《星际旅行》爱好者，在电影拍摄期间，她通过语音邮件对该角色发表了意见。<ref>{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|title=New 'Star Trek' Cast Took Cues From The Classic Series|work=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=2009-04-21|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1609732/story.jhtml|accessdate=2009-04-23|archive-date=2009-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422222133/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1609732/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> {{link-en|悉尼·泰米娅·布瓦特|Sydney Tamiia Poitier}}亦参与了该角色的试演。<ref>{{cite news|author=Jen Yamato |url=http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/comic_con_2007/news/1657693/exclusive_sydney_tamiia_poitier_on_critics_grindhouse_and_the_final_frontier |title=Sydney Tamiia Poitier on Critics, Grindhouse, and the Final Frontier |publisher=[[烂番茄|烂番茄]] |date=2007-08-01 |accessdate=2008-12-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227111229/http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/comic_con_2007/news/1657693/exclusive_sydney_tamiia_poitier_on_critics_grindhouse_and_the_final_frontier |archivedate=2009-02-27 }}</ref>

*[[西蒙·佩格|西蒙·佩格]]饰[[蒙哥马利·斯科特|蒙哥马利·斯科特（斯科提）]]。佩格是唯一没有经过试演的演员：艾布拉姆斯只是给他发了封邮件，问他是否有意出演这一角色。为了表现出斯科提的苏格兰口音，佩格在妻子莫琳（{{small|Maureen}}，苏格兰[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]人）的协助下开始了口音练习；不过，他觉得来自[[林利斯戈|林利斯戈]]的斯科提应更具有东岸口音，所以，在他后来的表演中，斯科提说着一口混合有两地口音的方言，但倾向于西部口音。<ref>{{cite news|author=Siobhan Synnot|title=Simon Pegg interview|work={{link-en|苏格兰周日报|Scotland on Sunday}}|date=2009-04-26|url=http://scotlandonsunday.scotsman.com/features/Simon-Pegg-interview.5204545.jp|accessdate=2009-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090429130148/http://scotlandonsunday.scotsman.com/features/Simon-Pegg-interview.5204545.jp|archive-date=2009-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同是格拉斯哥人的第一助理导演汤米·戈姆利（{{small|Tommy Gormley}}）也向他提供了帮助。<ref>{{cite news|author=Craig McLean|title=Simon Pegg can still boldly go ... to East Kilbride|work=[[星期日泰晤士报|星期日泰晤士报]]|date=2009-04-26|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article6168068.ece|accessdate=2009-04-26|archive-date=2009-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090518095609/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article6168068.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>佩格认为，斯科提是一名典型的苏格兰人物，他说道：“在饮酒打架后，苏格兰人［Scots，译注］将是第一个大声嘲笑自己的人。”<ref>原文：“Scots are the first people to laugh at the fact that they drink and fight a bit”．</ref>其中斯科特的昵称“斯科提”（{{small|Scotty}}）正是“Scots”（苏格兰人）的变体。几年前，佩格在《{{link-en|屋事生非|Spaced}}》中的角色曾经嘲笑说，每部奇数号的《星际旅行》电影都“拍得烂”（{{small|shit}}）才是人生的真谛。佩格自嘲道：“命运让我出现在这部电影中，来证明我自己是在说屁话。”<ref>{{cite news|author=Erin Biba|title=Simon Pegg's Geek Roots Show in Spaced|work=[[连线_(杂志)|连线]]|date=2008-07-21|url=http://www.wired.com/underwire/2008/07/simon-peggs-gee/|accessdate=2008-10-02|quote=Fate put me in the movie to show me I was talking out of my ass.|archive-date=2012-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106233435/http://www.wired.com/underwire/2008/07/simon-peggs-gee|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*[[赵约翰|赵约翰]]（或譯“周約翰”）饰[[苏鲁光|苏鲁光]]。艾布拉姆斯顾虑于让一名韩裔美国人出演日裔角色，但[[乔治·武井|乔治·武井]]劝说道：苏鲁是进取号上所有亚洲人的代表。于是，艾布拉姆斯决定让赵约翰出演这一角色。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsarama.com/film/010921-Takei-2.html|title=From 'Trek' to 'Wars', Part 2: George Takei on Star Trek|author=Steve Fritz|publisher=Newsarama|date=2009-01-21|accessdate=2009-01-22|archive-date=2009-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124003819/http://newsarama.com/film/010921-Takei-2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>赵约翰同意出演这名亚裔角色：“有一些动作角色你是决不会得到的，比如去扮演一名牛仔。［出演苏鲁］圆了我的梦——迈入太空吧。”<ref>原文：“there are certain acting roles that you are never going to get, and one of them is playing a cowboy. [Playing Sulu] is a realization of that dream — going into space.”</ref>他认为角色的阳刚气质非常重要，并为此进行了两周的搏击训练。<ref>{{cite news | title = John John Cho: Sulu Is A Badass | work = TrekMovie | date = 2007-12-16 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2007/12/16/john-cho-sulus-a-badass/ | accessdate = 2008-02-16 | archive-date = 2008-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080220161240/http://trekmovie.com/2007/12/16/john-cho-sulus-a-badass/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>在拍摄期间，赵约翰的手腕意外受伤，不过其代理人称其“并无大碍”。<ref>{{cite news | author = Anthony Pascale | title = Cho Injured On Trek Set | work = TrekMovie | date = 2008-03-17 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/03/17/cho-injured-on-trek-set-talks-a-bit-of-trek/ | accessdate = 2008-03-19 | quote = no big deal | archive-date = 2008-03-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080320034741/http://trekmovie.com/2008/03/17/cho-injured-on-trek-set-talks-a-bit-of-trek/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{link-en|詹姆斯·凯森·李|James Kyson Lee}}也曾有意出演这一角色，但由于当时昆图已经决定出演斯波克，电视剧《[[英雄_(电视剧)|英雄]]》的制片方不希望再让一名演员离开三个月之久。<ref>{{cite news | author = Ileane Rudolph | title = Heroes Preview: Ando's Secret Superpower Desire | work = [[电视指南|电视指南]] | date = 2007-10-29 | url = http://www.tvguide.com/news/heroes-preview-ando-39658.aspx | accessdate = 2007-10-31 | archive-date = 2009-04-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090428133352/http://www.tvguide.com/news/heroes-preview-ando-39658.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>

*[[安東·葉爾欽|安東·葉爾欽]]飾演[[帕夫·切科夫|帕夫·切科夫]]：与其他演员不同，叶尔钦可以选择继承前任演员的哪些表演元素。叶尔钦决定继承{{link-en|沃尔特·凯尼格|Walter Koenig}}发音的方式，将“v”发音成“w”；尽管他与艾布拉姆斯都觉得这种发音更常见于波兰人，而不是俄罗斯人。<ref name=abramstrailer>{{cite web|title=JJ Abrams on the new Star Trek trailer|work=[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国在线]]|url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/jj-abrams-talks-star-trek-trailer|accessdate=2008-11-17|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025230427/http://www.empireonline.com/features/jj-abrams-talks-star-trek-trailer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他认为，切科夫是一个古怪的角色，是在“[[冷战|冷战]]中期”<ref>原文：“in the middle of the Cold War.”</ref>被故意加进电视剧里的俄罗斯人。他回顾说：“在他们与［说了］‘我就是阿波罗’的{{link-en|谁悼我主？|Who Mourns for Adonais?|阿波罗}}谈话时，切科夫就像是‘那我就是全俄罗斯人的[[沙皇|沙皇]]’一般。［……］他们让他说的这些话。我的意思是，他的确是最最古怪的一名角色。”<ref>{{cite news|author=Cindy White |title=Young Chekov Talks Trek |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2008-01-28 |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/847/847936p1.html |accessdate=2008-01-28 |quote=scene where they're talking to Apollo [who says], 'I am Apollo.' And Chekov is like, 'And I am the czar of all Russias.' [...] They gave him these lines. I mean he really is the weirdest, weirdest character. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080131173756/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/847/847936p1.html |archivedate=2008-01-31 }}</ref>

*[[埃里克·巴纳|埃里克·巴纳]]饰{{link-en|尼禄 (星际迷航)|Nero (Star Trek)|尼禄舰长}}，电影中的反派，来自未来的[[罗慕伦|罗慕伦人]]。巴纳的情节一直拍摄到了摄制工作结束。他“在小时候是一名超级星迷”，<ref>{{cite news | author = Shawn Adler | title = Eric Bana Boldly Goes On About New ‘Star Trek’ | work = [[MTV|MTV]] | date = 2008-02-11 | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/02/11/eric-bana-boldly-goes-on-about-new-star-trek/ | accessdate = 2008-02-12 | quote = a huge Trekkie when [he] was a kid | archive-date = 2009-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090318102013/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/02/11/eric-bana-boldly-goes-on-about-new-star-trek/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>但从未看过一部《星际旅行》电影。<ref>{{cite news|author=Brian Jacks|title=Eric Bana Has Never Seen A ‘Star Trek’ Movie|work=[[MTV|MTV]]电影网志|date=2009-05-05|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/05/05/eric-bana-has-never-seen-a-star-trek-movie/|accessdate=2009-05-06|archive-date=2009-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507074306/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/05/05/eric-bana-has-never-seen-a-star-trek-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管他“痴迷于原初-{}-系列”<ref>原文：“crazy about the original series”．</ref>，但只有是他觉得十分棒（{{small|awesome}}）的剧本，他才会接演其中的角色。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bana calls 'Star Trek' role irresistible|publisher=United Press International|date=2008-02-29|url=http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2008/02/29/Bana_calls_Star_Trek_role_irresistible/UPI-78451204318682/|accessdate=2008-10-13|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629153315/http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/2008/02/29/Bana_calls_Star_Trek_role_irresistible/UPI-78451204318682|dead-url=no}}</ref>巴纳認識艾布拉姆斯，因为他俩碰巧有着同一名经纪人。<ref>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Bana Spoofs Star Trek Plot Details|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2008-02-26|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/02/06/bana-talks-abrams-andjokes-plot-details/|accessdate=2008-10-13|archive-date=2008-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007165256/http://trekmovie.com/2008/02/06/bana-talks-abrams-andjokes-plot-details/|dead-url=no}}</ref>巴纳即兴发挥了该角色说话的方式。<ref>{{cite news|author=Peter Mitchell |title=Bana dons face tattoos for new role |publisher=ninemsn |date=2009-03-06 |url=http://news.ninemsn.com.au/entertainment/764546/bana-dons-face-tattoos-for-new-role |accessdate=2009-03-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090310091213/http://news.ninemsn.com.au/entertainment/764546/bana-dons-face-tattoos-for-new-role |archivedate=2009-03-10 }}</ref>

