*[[斯潘塞·丹尼尔斯|斯潘塞·丹尼尔斯]]饰约翰尼（{{small|Johnny}}），柯克儿童时期的一位朋友。在最初的设定中，丹尼尔斯饰演的是柯克的哥哥“山姆”——小乔治·塞缪尔·柯克（{{small|George Samuel "Sam" Kirk, Jr.}}）。然而，丹尼尔斯的场景后来大都被剪掉了；相应的，柯克的台词也被重新配音。<ref>{{cite web| author = Trotter, Charles| title = Meet The Young Kirk Boys| publisher = TrekMovie| date = 2008-01-29| url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/01/29/meet-the-young-kirk-boys/| accessdate = 2008-01-28| archive-date = 2009-04-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090407034228/http://trekmovie.com/2008/01/29/meet-the-young-kirk-boys/| dead-url = no}}</ref>

[[泰勒·佩里|泰勒·佩里]]饰[[星际舰队学院|星际舰队学院]]领导者理查德·巴尼特上将（{{small|Admiral Richard Barnett}}）。{{link-en|詹姆斯·考利|James Cawley}}饰[[星际舰队|星际舰队]]的一名军官。{{link-en|帕维尔·林奇尼考夫|Pavel Lychnikoff}}与{{link-en|露西娅·瑞科尔|Lucia Rijker}}饰罗慕伦人；其中，林奇尼考夫饰演一名中校，瑞科尔饰演通讯官。曾在《[[星际旅行VI：未来之城|星际旅行VI：未来之城]]》中饰演[[克林贡|克林贡人]]的{{link-en|威廉·摩根·谢泼德|W. Morgan Sheppard}}，在此部电影中饰演瓦肯科学委员会（{{small|Vulcan Science Council}}）的领导者。《星际旅行》爱好者、[[卡内基梅隆大学|卡内基梅隆大学]]教授[[兰迪·保施|兰迪·保施]]（于2008年7月25日逝世）在片中饰演开尔文号的一名船员，并有一段对白。<ref>{{cite news|author=Charles Trotter|title=Fun Stuff In Official Star Trek Movie Credits|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2009-05-02|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/05/02/fun-stuff-in-official-star-trek-movie-credits/|accessdate=2009-05-04|archive-date=2009-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505151722/http://trekmovie.com/2009/05/02/fun-stuff-in-official-star-trek-movie-credits/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《星际旅行》创始人[[吉恩·罗登伯里|吉恩·罗登伯里]]的遗孀{{link-en|玛婕尔·巴雷特|Majel Barrett}}再度为进取号的计算机配音；2008年12月18日，亦即完成配音工作的两个星期后，玛婕尔逝世。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/breakingnews/ci_11263728|title=Majel Roddenberry, widow of 'Trek' creator, dies |last=Jablon |first=Robert |date=2008-12-18|work=San Jose Mercury-News |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=2008-12-18}}</ref>为了表达对玛婕尔与吉恩·罗登伯里夫妇的尊敬，这部电影向他们进行了题献。<ref name=abramsiesb />

奥利奇与库兹曼为[[威廉·夏特纳|威廉·夏特纳]]撰写了一段情节，其中，老斯波克将从前时间线中柯克录制的信息转交给了年轻的自己。“大概就是生日上的愿望，了解到斯波克将要前往罗穆卢斯星，而柯克当时可能已经死了。”<ref>原文：“It was basically a Happy Birthday wish knowing that Spock was going to go off to Romulus, and Kirk would probably be dead by the time”．</ref>而“[[前人所未至的领域|前人所未至的领域]]”原本也是打算让夏特纳朗诵的。<ref name=shatscameo>{{cite news|author=Meredith Woerner|title=The Shatner Scene You Never Saw In Abrams' Star Trek|work=io9|date=2009-05-11|url=http://io9.com/5249752/the-shatner-scene-you-never-saw-in-abrams-star-trek|accessdate=2009-05-12|archive-date=2009-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514060119/http://io9.com/5249752/the-shatner-scene-you-never-saw-in-abrams-star-trek|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，夏特纳希望分享尼莫伊的主角戏份，而不希望只去露个面。<ref>{{cite news|author=Clayton Neuman|title=Masters of SciFi - J.J. Abrams on Reviving Frankenstein in Fringe and Adhering to Canon With Star Trek|publisher=AMC|date=2008-09-08|url=http://blogs.amctv.com/scifi-scanner/2008/09/jj-abrams-interview.php|accessdate=2008-09-09|archive-date=2008-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220175109/http://blogs.amctv.com/scifi-scanner/2008/09/jj-abrams-interview.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于他的角色已在《[[星际旅行VII：日换星移|星际旅行VII：日换星移]]》中死去，他因而建议电影将{{link-en|回归 (星际旅行)|Return (Star Trek)|柯克复活的小说}}正典化。<ref>{{cite news | author = William Keck | title = Celeb Watch: Shatner's gone there before, but new 'Trek' isn't on frontier | work = [[今日美国|今日美国]] | date = 2008-01-21 | url = http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-01-28-shatner_n.htm | accessdate = 2008-03-26 | archive-date = 2012-03-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316134006/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/celebwatch/2008-01-28-shatner_n.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>然而，艾布拉姆斯决定不让他与尼莫伊一同出现，否则就会让这部电影成为柯克复活的电影，而非引入新版角色的电影。<ref name=abramsiesb>{{cite news|author=Christina Radish |title=Interview: J.J. Abrams on Star Trek |work=IESB |date=2009-04-26 |url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6786&Itemid=99 |accessdate=2009-04-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430001932/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=6786&Itemid=99 |archivedate=2009-04-30 }}</ref>尼莫伊并不喜欢《日换星移》中让该角色死亡的设定，但觉得令柯克复活亦会不利于这部电影。<ref name="grandslam">{{cite news | author = Vic Holtreman | title = Hungry For More Star Trek Details? Here You Go! | publisher = Screen Rant | date = 2008-04-13 | url = http://screenrant.com/hungry-for-more-star-trek-details-here-you-go-vic-1511/ | accessdate = 2008-04-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080802120254/http://screenrant.com/hungry-for-more-star-trek-details-here-you-go-vic-1511/ | archivedate = 2008-08-02 }}</ref>

[[尼切尔·尼科尔斯|尼切尔·尼科尔斯]]希望扮演乌乎拉的祖母，但由于[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|编剧协会大罢工]]的影响，艾布拉姆斯无法将她的情节写入剧本当中。<ref>{{cite news|author=Greg Parker|title=Nichelle Nichols Almost Had ‘Star Trek’ Cameo?|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2008-06-29|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/06/29/nichelle-nichols-almost-had-star-trek-cameo/|accessdate=2008-06-30|archive-date=2008-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630161404/http://trekmovie.com/2008/06/29/nichelle-nichols-almost-had-star-trek-cameo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾布拉姆斯还有意让[[凯莉·罗素|凯莉·罗素]]出演，但他们都觉得他想要她演的角色与她曾演过的其他角色太相像了。<ref>{{cite news|author=Robert Sanchez|url=http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3688&Itemid=99|title=Keri Russell Talks Star Trek|publisher=IESB|date=2007-11-10|accessdate=2008-12-28|archive-date=2009-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104140508/http://www.iesb.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=3688&Itemid=99|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 制作 ==
=== 发展 ===
{{quote|以下是[[吉恩·罗登伯里|吉恩［·罗登伯里］]]在1991年8月逝世前在一次采访中说的内容：有人曾经问过他：‘《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》在未来将如何发展？’他回答说他希望有朝一日，有一群聪明的年轻人能够在一起再做一次，并比他做得更大更好。他祝福他们。<br />——理查德·阿诺德，罗登伯里的助手<ref>{{cite news|author=Jay A. Fernandez |title='Star Trek': Enterprise marketing |work=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] |date=2009-02-19 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3iffc4c7c167527636db975bf1b21d20cb?pn=2 |accessdate=2009-03-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223094050/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3iffc4c7c167527636db975bf1b21d20cb?pn=2 |archivedate=2009-02-23 |deadurl=yes }}<br />Here's what Gene [Roddenberry] said in an interview just before he died in August 1991; somebody had asked him, 'What's going to become of ''Star Trek'' in the future?' And he said that he hoped that some day some bright young thing would come along and do it again, bigger and better than he had ever done it. And he wished them well. — Richard Arnold, Roddenberry's assistant
</ref>}}

在1968年的[[世界科幻大会|世界科幻大会]]上，《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》的创始人[[吉恩·罗登伯里|吉恩·罗登伯里]]宣布说，他将制作一出[[星际旅行：原初系列|电视剧]]的电影[[前传|前传]]。<ref>{{cite book|author=Judith and Garfield Reeves-Stevens|title=The Art of Star Trek|url=https://archive.org/details/artofstartrek0000reev_z0h2|publisher=[[口袋书店|口袋书店]]|page=[https://archive.org/details/artofstartrek0000reev_z0h2/page/155 155]|date=1995|isbn=0-671-89804-3}}</ref>1980年代，{{link-en|拉尔夫·温特 (制片人)|Ralph Winter (producer)|拉尔夫·温特}}与[[哈维·贝内特|哈维·贝内特]]在发展[[星际旅行IV：抢救未来|第四部]]与[[星际旅行VI：未来之城|第六部]]电影时，曾两度重新提出前传的概念。再往后，{{link-en|戴维·拉菲里 (制片人)|David Loughery|戴维·拉菲里}}曾写出了名为《学院年代》（{{small|''The Academy Years''}}）的剧本，但由于原有演员与爱好者的强烈反对而告罢。2005年2月，随着第十部电影《[[星际旅行X：复仇女神|星际旅行X：复仇女神]]》（2002年）的失败以及电视剧《[[星际旅行：进取号|星际旅行：进取号]]》的停播，星旅系列的执行制片人[[赖克·伯曼|赖克·伯曼]]与剧作家{{link-en|埃里克·廷德森|Erik Jendresen}}开始发展一部新的电影《星际旅行》（{{small|''Star Trek''}}）。他们打算在电影中启用全新设定的角色，并让柯克的祖先泰比里厄斯·蔡斯（{{small|Tiberius Chase}}）主演。电影将发生在《进取号》之后，初-{}-代之前，大概处于地球-罗慕伦战争期间。<ref>{{cite book|author=David Hughes|title=The Greatest Science Fiction Movies Never Made|publisher=Titan Books|date=2008|pages=35, 37, 44–46|isbn=9781845767556}}</ref>

2005年，[[派拉蒙电影公司|派拉蒙电影公司]]的拥有者[[維亞康姆|維亞康姆]]从[[CBS公司|CBS公司]]中分离了出来，它保留了[[派拉蒙|派拉蒙]]的电视广播财产，其中包括“''Star Trek''”商标的所有权。时任派拉蒙公司总裁的{{link-en|盖尔·伯曼|Gail Berman}}说服了CBS的首席执行官{{link-en|莱斯利·穆维斯|Leslie Moonves}}，并得到了他的许可：在CBS收回权利以开发新一部电视剧前，他们将有18个月时间来发展一部新的《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》电影（作为回报，CBS将保留商品化权）。伯曼向《[[谍中谍3|谍中谍3]]》的编剧[[罗伯托·奥利奇|罗伯托·奥利奇]]与[[亚历克斯·库兹曼|亚历克斯·库兹曼]]征求了对新电影的意见；在《[[谍中谍3|谍中谍3]]》拍摄完毕后，伯曼邀请其导演[[J·J·艾布拉姆斯|J·J·艾布拉姆斯]]来制作新电影。<ref name=nytimes>{{cite news|author=Dave Itzkoff|title=New team retrofits old ship|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2009-04-23|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/26/movies/26itzk.html?_r=3&pagewanted=all|accessdate=2009-04-26|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308190539/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/26/movies/26itzk.html?_r=3&pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾布拉姆斯、奥利奇和库兹曼以及制片人[[戴蒙·林德洛夫|戴蒙·林德洛夫]]和[[布赖恩·伯克|布赖恩·伯克]]都觉得，这一系列在此前的电视剧和电影中都已探索得足够多了；<ref name=transcript />他们还觉得部分{{link-en|星际旅行小说列表|List of Star Trek novels|《星际旅行》小说}}具有成为正典的价值，尽管吉恩·罗登伯里从未考虑过将这些小说提升为[[星际旅行正典|正典]]。<ref>{{cite news|author=Steve Krutzler |url=http://trekweb.com/articles/2006/06/07/Abrams-Cohorts-Emphasize-Respect-for-Mythology.shtml |title=Abrams Cohorts Emphasize Respect for Mythology in ''Trek XI'', Say Script Will Contain Old and New |publisher=TrekWeb |date=2006-06-07 |accessdate=2006-08-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060709134818/http://trekweb.com/articles/2006/06/07/Abrams-Cohorts-Emphasize-Respect-for-Mythology.shtml |archivedate=2006-07-09 }}</ref>在创作小组中，奥利奇和林德洛夫自视为{{link-en|星迷|trekkie}}，<ref name=orcithetrekkie>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Interview - Roberto Orci On Why He Is A Trekkie & Making Trek Big Again|publisher=TrekMovie|date=2007-10-04|url=http://trekmovie.com/2007/10/04/interview-roberto-orci-on-why-he-is-a-trekkie/|accessdate=2008-09-20|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701181219/http://trekmovie.com/2007/10/04/interview-roberto-orci-on-why-he-is-a-trekkie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>库兹曼是一名普通的爱好者，而伯克则不是。<ref name=new />艾布拉姆斯的[[坏机器人制片公司|坏机器人制片公司]]与派拉蒙共同制作了这部电影，这是第一次由另一家公司为《星际旅行》电影的制作提供资金支持。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://trekmovie.com/2007/12/05/paramount-updates-star-trek-credits-official-synopsis-adds-production-partner/ | title=Paramount Updates Star Trek Credits & Official Synopsis + Adds Production Partner | publisher= | date=2007-12-05 | accessdate=2007-12-09 | archive-date=2021-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308151414/https://trekmovie.com/2007/12/05/paramount-updates-star-trek-credits-official-synopsis-adds-production-partner/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>{{link-en|小比尔·托德曼|Bill Todman Jr.}}的{{link-en|一级娱乐|Level 1 Entertainment}}公司亦曾是电影的合作制片方，但在2008年其融资伙伴的位置被{{link-en|望远镜娱乐公司|Spyglass Entertainment}}取代。<ref>{{cite news|title=Super High Resolution Images For ‘Star Trek’ 2009|publisher=|date=2008-12-30|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/12/30/super-high-resolution-images-for-star-trek-2009/|accessdate=2008-12-31|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307221344/https://trekmovie.com/2008/12/30/super-high-resolution-images-for-star-trek-2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

艾布拉姆斯没有看过《[[星际旅行X：复仇女神|星际旅行X：复仇女神]]》，因为他认为这一系列和他“毫无关联”（{{small|disconnected}}），<ref>{{cite news|title=Can J.J. Abrams save Star Trek?|work=[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]|date=2006年7月|page=56}}</ref>对他而言，《星际旅行》是关于柯克与斯波克的故事，其他的系列只是“使用了《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》之名但并无联系的太空探险”。<ref>原文：“separate space adventure[s] with the name ''Star Trek''”．</ref>艾布拉姆斯在小时候还很喜欢《[[星球大战IV：新希望|星球大战]]》。<ref>{{cite news|author=Matthew Leyland|title=Bold New Enterprise|work={{link-en|完全电影|Total Film}}|date=2009年4月|page=72}}</ref>他提到，他对《星际旅行》的常识使他得以制作出一部能将该系列介绍给新观众的电影；<ref name=questproblem>{{cite news|author=Geoff Boucher|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2009/01/star-trek-direc.html|title=J.J. Abrams on tribbles and the 'Galaxy Quest' problem|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|date=2009-01-29|accessdate=2009-01-29|archive-date=2009-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090316073542/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2009/01/star-trek-direc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而且，作为一名乐观的人，他觉得《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》的乐观色彩将与《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士]]》一类电影形成鲜明的对比。<ref name=new />他还说到，他喜欢《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》以探索为主的主题，也喜欢[[最高指导原则|最高指导原则]]禁止星际舰队干涉原始世界发展的理念。然而，艾布拉姆斯认为原初-{}-系列的预算限制让他们“没有足够的资源去真正表现探险的主题”。<ref>原文：“never had the resources to actually show the adventure”．</ref><ref name=empire>{{cite news|author=James Dyer|title=The Prime Director|work=[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]|date=2009年5月|pages=76-79}}</ref>他提到，他当初加入这一计划的原因，是因为他想要帮助奥利奇、库兹曼和林德洛夫。<ref name=nytimes />

2007年2月23日，[[JJ亞伯拉罕|艾布拉姆斯]]接受了派拉蒙执导此部电影的邀请，但依然只挂有制片人的头衔。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3idc516528ddd1b4263febcf5c67efa0ce | title = Abrams takes helm of ''Star Trek'' | work = [[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]] | date = 2007-02-24 | accessdate = 2008-04-14 | author = Tatiana Siegel | archive-date = 2008-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080516211316/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3idc516528ddd1b4263febcf5c67efa0ce | dead-url = no }}</ref>在读过剧本后，他描述说：“我将对那些插手并执导这部电影的人嫉妒万分。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Abrams Talks Trek, Cloverfield 2 |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2008-05-16 |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/874/874629p1.html |accessdate=2008-05-16 |quote=I would be so agonizingly envious of whoever stepped in and directed the movie. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081018234327/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/874/874629p1.html |archivedate=2008-10-18 }}</ref>奥利奇与库兹曼认为，他们故事的目标是给艾布拉姆斯一样的普通爱好者留下印象。<ref name=impact>{{cite news|author=Hugh Hart|title=Star Trek Writers Brace for Impact|work=[[连线_(杂志)|连线]]|date=2008-10-02|url=http://www.wired.com/underwire/2008/10/star-trek-write/|accessdate=2008-10-03|archive-date=2013-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628123922/http://www.wired.com/underwire/2008/10/star-trek-write/|dead-url=no}}</ref>即使在拍摄过程中，[[JJ·亞伯拉罕|艾布拉姆斯]]依然紧张于“所有的这些纹脸和尖耳朵，稀奇古怪的武器和罗慕伦的语言，以及关于‘中立区’和‘星际舰队’的对话［。但］我知道这会成功，因为亚历克斯［·库兹曼］和鲍勃［·奥利奇］的剧本是如此富于感情且如此值得一述。刚开始这段旅程时我并不喜欢柯克和斯波克——但我现在深爱着他们。”<ref>原文：“with all these tattooed faces and pointy ears, bizarre weaponry and Romulan linguists, with dialogue about 'Neutral Zones' and 'Starfleet' [but] I knew this would work, because the script Alex and Bob wrote was so emotional and so relatable. I didn't love Kirk and Spock when I began this journey – but I love them now.”</ref><ref name=new />

=== 编剧 ===
{{quote box|width=40%|quote=“我们来自不同的世界，亚历克斯［·库兹曼］出生于此，我则出生在[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]，并在九岁前都一直在那里生活。柯克与斯波克则来自两个完全相反的世界。简而言之，这就是我们。我们被对方所吸引，被我们缺乏的东西所吸引。电影的故事围绕着两名如此对立的人物展开，他们对立的程度足以让他们扼死对方；然而，他们却团结一心、并肩成长。这就是我们。我们会并肩进入[[曲速|曲速]]。”|source=罗伯托·奥利奇对电影情感内容的谈话<ref>原文：“We're from different worlds, Alex [Kurtzman] was born here, and I was born in Mexico City and lived there until I was nine. Kirk and Spock are opposites from two worlds. That's us in a nutshell. We're drawn to each by what each of us lacks. The story of this film is about two guys who are such opposites that they might end up strangling each other but instead they bond and thrive together. That's us. We can go warp speed together.”</ref><ref name=cling />}}

奥利奇认为，创作一出全新的[[外传|外传]]将是无礼的，<ref name=strongwomen />而让[[伦纳德·尼莫伊|伦纳德·尼莫伊]]加入影片则是非常重要的：“和他一起围坐在营火旁时，他会不停地和你分享他的记忆”。<ref>原文：“Having him sitting around a camp fire sharing his memories was never gonna cut it”．</ref>时间旅行的情节在最初便被打算纳入电影当中。<ref name=canonandrealscience>{{cite news|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/12/11/bob-orci-explains-how-the-new-star-trek-movie-fits-with-trek-canon-and-real-science/|title=Bob Orci Explains How The New Star Trek Movie Fits With Trek Canon (and Real Science)|publisher=|author=Anthony Pascale|date=2008-12-11|accessdate=2008-12-23|format=Some information is taken from subsequent comments by Orci under the username "boborci"|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330153411/http://trekmovie.com/2008/12/11/bob-orci-explains-how-the-new-star-trek-movie-fits-with-trek-canon-and-real-science/|dead-url=no}}</ref>库兹曼加入的时间旅行情节创造了危机感，而不像其他[[前传|前传]]那样让观众们已经“知道他们是怎么死的”。<ref>原文：“know how they all died”．</ref><ref name=died>{{cite news|author=Patrick Lee|title=Orci & Kurtzman: Why they don't call Star Trek a reboot|work=[[科幻电报|科幻电报]]|date=2009-03-26|url=http://scifiwire.com/2009/03/orci-kurtzman-why-they-do.php|accessdate=2009-03-26|archive-date=2009-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327230950/http://scifiwire.com/2009/03/orci-kurtzman-why-they-do.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>编剧们认为，尽管时间旅行的情节在以往的《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》中已经被用滥了，但它却能巧妙地达成让原始角色进行新一轮探险的目的，同时还能完全避免其他电影的影响。<ref name=okgeekmonthly />艾布拉姆斯选择了[[罗慕伦人|罗慕伦人]]作为电影的反派角色，因为他们在该系列节目中的出场时间要少于[[克林贡|克林贡人]]，而且让柯克在电视剧以前便遇上罗慕伦人将“十分有趣”（{{small|fun}}）。<ref>{{cite news|author=Helen O'Hara|title=Klingon Subplot Revealed|work=[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]|date=2008-11-14|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23656|accessdate=2008-11-14|archive-date=2012-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119044339/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=23656|dead-url=no}}</ref>奥利奇与库兹曼提到，既然克林贡人在后来的《[[星艦迷航記|星际旅行]]》系列中已被塑造成了英雄，再将他们魔鬼化则是退步的行为；然而，罗慕伦人的出现却能延续斯波克的故事：按照年代顺序，斯波克最后一次出现在《[[星际旅行：下一代|星际旅行：下一代]]》的{{《}}{{TNG|Unification}}{{》}}一集中，设定年份为2368年。<ref name=okgeekmonthly>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Star Trek Writers Alex Kurtzman & Roberto Orci|work=TrekMovie|date=2009-04-30|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/04/30/interview-roberto-orci-alex-kurtzman/|accessdate=2009-05-01|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307223537/https://trekmovie.com/2009/04/30/interview-roberto-orci-alex-kurtzman/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在原始连续性的{{《}}{{TOS|Balance of Terror}}{{》}}一集中，柯克成为了第一名看见罗慕伦人的人类；而这一集亦影响了此部电影。<ref name=orcithetrekkie />奥利奇说，如果不施加一些巧妙手法的话，将很难给时间旅行提供一个充足的理由；譬如让尼禄蓄意追杀柯克的理由。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://link.brightcove.com/services/player/bcpid17054225001?bclid=18291076001&bctid=18271280001|title=Star Trek: Behind the scenes|work=[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]|format=Video|accessdate=2009-04-03|archive-date=2009-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415040603/http://link.brightcove.com/services/player/bcpid17054225001?bclid=18291076001&bctid=18271280001|dead-url=no}}</ref>

奥利奇提到，尽管在这出时间旅行的故事中，他们可以修改部分背景故事的元素，譬如柯克与罗慕伦人的第一次相遇；然而，他们并不能借此改掉所有的设定，他们试图让这部电影表现得更像前传。在初-{}-代的{{《}}{{TOS|Obsession}}{{》}}一集中，柯克曾在法拉格特号上服役；这一重要设定因被认为与柯克和斯波克相遇的故事无关而省略掉了。<ref name="canonandrealscience" />此外，电影原本还安排有柯克与童年时期的卡罗尔·马库斯相遇的情节，后者在《[[星际旅行II：可汗怒吼|星际旅行II：可汗怒吼]]》中曾以柯克之子的母亲身份出现；然而由于电影需要用更多的时间来介绍核心角色，该段场景最后被移到第12集。<ref name=shatscameo /><ref name=carolmarcus>{{cite news|author=Patrick Lee|title=Orci & Kurtzman: What familiar Star Trek bits will you see in the new movie?|work=[[科幻电报|科幻电报]]|date=2009-03-24|url=http://scifiwire.com/2009/03/orci-kurtzman-what-famili.php|accessdate=2009-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327025320/http://scifiwire.com/2009/03/orci-kurtzman-what-famili.php|archive-date=2009-03-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>要解释清楚船员们为何能再度齐聚并不容易，奥利奇和库兹曼原本打算通过老斯波克来解释时间线会自行修复的原理，并希望借此加强电影关于命运的主题；然而，由于有关的场景难以撰写，这一设想最终被放弃了。<ref name=okgeekmonthly /><ref name=creativescreenwriting />

电影的制片人们在《[[最高指导原则_(电影)|最高指导原则]]》《{{link-en|斯波克的世界|Spock's World}}》以及《完美命运》（{{small|Best Destiny}}）等小说中获得了灵感，填补了正典中尚未解释的空白；《完美命运》详细地探究柯克的童年生活，并提及了其父母的名字。<ref name=orcithetrekkie /><ref name=canonandrealscience /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20234010,00.html|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|author=Jeff Jensen|title=Inspirations for a whole new ''Enterprise''|date=2008-10-17|accessdate=2008-12-15|archive-date=2009-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090105205736/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20234010,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>小说中关于[[联邦星舰进取号_(NCC-1701)|进取号]]建造于地球的设定亦被收纳入电影当中，许多爱好者曾根据该设定创作了多幅进取号在船坞中建造的画作。奥利奇将这些爱好者的画作寄送给了艾布拉姆斯，以向其说明这部电影所能达到的真实程度。<ref name=orcilatest/>奥利奇解释说：由于船舰将使用[[人造重力|人造重力]]并需维持[[曲速引擎|曲速飞行]]，在被模拟的{{link-en|重力井|gravity well}}原址校准船舰上的设备乃是最佳的做法；因此，船舰的部分结构将在地球上建造。<ref name="orci"/>因为正典中对该舰是否建造于[[旧金山|旧金山]]含糊其辞，他们决定在[[艾奥瓦州|艾奥瓦州]]建造这艘星舰；但也解释说，星舰的建造地点没有重复原始时间线中的设定，而这正是时间旅行的结果。<ref name=died />艾布拉姆斯还提到，初-{}-代节目中的连续性有时也会不一致。<ref name=wondercon />

奥利奇和库兹曼说，他们去掉了“{{link-en|星际科技泡泡|Treknobabble}}”，让电影的内容更加丰富有趣，并将电影命名为简洁的“Star Trek”（从而让新观众意识到，他们不需要去预习其他任何一部电影），这一切都是为了让普通观众与爱好者们同样喜欢这部电影。<ref name="nosubtitles">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1554046/story.jhtml|work=[[MTV|MTV]]|title='Star Trek' Writers Talk Direction, Technobabble — But Not Matt Damon|date=2007-03-08|accessdate=2007-08-07|author=Josh Horowitz|archive-date=2007-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310162811/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1554046/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾布拉姆斯认为，幽默和性是这部电影中必不可少的成分，从而应该保留下来。<ref name=questproblem />奥利奇认为，在电影中做到真实与做到严肃是两码事。<ref name=orcilatest>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Exclusive Interview: Roberto Orci On All The Latest With Star Trek (and more)|publisher=|date=2008-12-10|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/12/09/exclusive-interview-roberto-orci-on-all-the-latest-with-star-trek-and-more/|accessdate=2008-12-09|archive-date=2017-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714085432/http://trekmovie.com/2008/12/09/exclusive-interview-roberto-orci-on-all-the-latest-with-star-trek-and-more/|dead-url=no}}</ref>艾布拉姆斯、伯克、林德洛夫与库兹曼都是《可汗怒吼》的爱好者，他们同时还提到说，《下一代》的{{《}}{{TNG|Yesterday's Enterprise}}{{》}}一集也对本部电影有所影响。<ref name=orcithetrekkie />艾布拉姆斯的妻子凯蒂（{{small|Katie}}）经常为剧本提供建议，而奥利奇、库兹曼与林德洛夫的妻子们亦为强化片中的女性角色提供了很多意见。<ref name=strongwomen />凯蒂·艾布拉姆斯对电影中的强势女性角色表示认可，因而劝说其丈夫签约导演。<ref name=grandorci>{{cite news | author = Anthony Pascale | title = Grand Slam XVI: Highlights From Orci Q&A | work = TrekMovie | date = 2008-04-13 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/04/13/grand-slam-xvi-highlights-from-orci-qa/ | accessdate = 2008-04-13 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308071900/https://trekmovie.com/2008/04/13/grand-slam-xvi-highlights-from-orci-qa/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

为了寻求灵感，奥利奇和库兹曼还阅读了一些关于该系列的研究院论文；<ref name=transcript />他们提到了关于柯克、斯波克与麦科伊和[[威廉·莎士比亚|莎士比亚式]]典型人物的比较，还提到柯克与斯波克的友情类似于[[约翰·列侬|约翰·列侬]]和[[保罗·麦卡特尼|保罗·麦卡特尼]]的友情。<ref name=orcithetrekkie />他们还说，在电影的创作过程中，他们受到了《星球大战》的影响，特别是节奏方面的影响。奥利奇说：“我要感受太空，我要感受速度，我要感受一切，但如果《星际迷航》变得十分庄重的话，我的这些感觉就会有一些失落”。<ref>原文：“I want to feel the space, I want to feel speed and I want to feel all the things that can become a little bit lost when ''Star Trek'' becomes very stately”．</ref><ref name=impact />他们在撰写动作场景时融入了《星球大战》的元素，<ref name=died />伯克提到，柯克与斯波克最初的冷漠关系正是“当他们刚开始旅程时，[[韩·索罗|韩·索罗]]不与任何人为友”的映照。<ref>{{cite news|author=Bryan Cairns|title=To Boldy Go ... 'Star Trek' Executive Producer Bryan Burk|publisher=Newsarama|date=2009-03-23|url=http://www.newsarama.com/film/090323-star-trek-bryan-burk.html|accessdate=2009-03-23|quote=Han Solo wasn't friends with anyone when they started on their journey.|archive-date=2009-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327120533/http://www.newsarama.com/film/090323-star-trek-bryan-burk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在片中，斯波克与乌乎拉建立了真正的关系，这默认了早期电视剧中乌乎拉对斯波克的兴趣。<ref name=creativescreenwriting>{{cite web|url=http://creativescreenwritingmagazine.blogspot.com/2009/05/star-trek-q.html|title=Star Trek Q&A|work=Creative Screenwriting|accessdate=2009-05-16|archive-date=2010-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101019061838/http://creativescreenwritingmagazine.blogspot.com/2009/05/star-trek-q.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>奥利奇希望引入一名强势的[[星际舰队|星际舰队]]舰长，他也同意采访者的意见，认为其他电影中用来陪衬柯克的舰长大部分都是“懦夫”（{{small|patsies}}）。<ref name=strongwomen>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Interview - Orci Talks Casting, Characters, Canon and Kirks|publisher=|date=2007-10-08|url=http://trekmovie.com/2007/10/08/interview-orci-talks-casting-characters-canon-and-more/|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211025108/https://trekmovie.com/2007/10/08/interview-orci-talks-casting-characters-canon-and-more/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

柯克父亲服役的联邦星舰开尔文号（{{small|USS ''Kelvin''}}），其名称来自艾布拉姆斯祖父的名字以及[[威廉·汤姆森|开尔文男爵]]发明的[[开尔文|开尔文]]温标。开尔文号的舰长理查德·罗博（{{link-en|法兰·塔希尔|Faran Tahir}}）的名字来源于奥利奇的[[古巴|古巴]]叔叔；奥利奇解释说，该虚构角色出生于古巴并成长于中东地区。<ref name=orcilatest />艾布拉姆斯此前作品中的“Slusho”亦出现在了本部电影中：乌乎拉在见到柯克的酒吧就点了一杯“Slusho”饮料。艾布拉姆斯在其电视剧《[[双面女间谍|双面女间谍]]》中创造了这种虚构的饮料，在电影《[[苜蓿地|苜蓿地]]》的[[病毒营销|病毒营销]]中亦有出现。“Slusho”的拥有者“Tagruato”同样出自《苜蓿地》，并出现在[[旧金山|旧金山]]的一座建筑上。<ref name=blink />电影中的红物质是一种红色的球体，亦是艾布拉姆斯拍片的一大特色，可以追溯到《双面女间谍》的试播集。<ref name=chamblissmagazinepreview>{{cite news|title=Star Trek Magazine #17 Preview + Scott Chambliss Interview Extract|publisher=|date=2009-03-20|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/03/20/star-trek-magazine-17-preview-scott-chambliss-interview-extract/|accessdate=2009-03-20|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308091315/https://trekmovie.com/2009/03/20/star-trek-magazine-17-preview-scott-chambliss-interview-extract/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 设计 ===
{{link-en|瑞安·丘奇 (概念艺术家)|Ryan Church (concept artist)|瑞安·丘奇}}、{{link-en|苜蓿地怪兽|Clover (creature)|《苜蓿地》怪兽}}的创造者内维尔·佩奇（{{small|Neville Page}}），<ref name=abramstrailer />以及《星际旅行》的老手{{link-en|约翰·伊夫斯|John Eaves}}<ref>{{cite news| url=http://trekmovie.com/2007/10/17/trekmoviecom-update-on-latest-shatner-enterprise-and-casting-rumors/| title=TrekMovie.com Update On Latest Shatner and Enterprise Rumors| publisher=| date=2007-10-17| accessdate=2007-10-18| archive-date=2021-01-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117102240/https://trekmovie.com/2007/10/17/trekmoviecom-update-on-latest-shatner-enterprise-and-casting-rumors/| dead-url=no}}</ref>是此部电影的主要设计人。艾布拉姆斯提到，由于许多现代科技都是受初-{}-代电视剧启发而发明，要再去描绘初-{}-代电视剧中的未来将会非常困难，甚而可能会让它显得十分过时。因此，电影的设计不仅要与电视剧相一致，还要让人感到它比电视剧之后真实世界的新发明更为先进。<ref name="transcript">{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Star Trek Cast & Crew Fan Chat Transcript + Pictures From The Set|publisher=|date=2008-01-25|url=http://trekmovie.com/2008/01/25/jj-abrams-trek-team-fan-chat-transcript-pictures-from-the-set/|accessdate=2008-01-27|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307195446/https://trekmovie.com/2008/01/25/jj-abrams-trek-team-fan-chat-transcript-pictures-from-the-set/|dead-url=no}}</ref>“我们已经有了比{{link-en|通讯器 (星际旅行)|communicator (Star Trek)|通讯器}}更为强大的[[iPhone|iPhone]]”<ref>原文：“We all have the iPhone that does more than the communicator”．</ref>，艾布拉姆斯说到，“我觉得有些过时的东西是你无法真正坚持的。如果你反倒觉得这些东西是真实的话，它们更应该被摒弃。”<ref>{{cite news|author=Fred Topel |title=J.J. Abrams on TV's Fringe |publisher=Suicide Girls |date=2008-09-05 |url=http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/J.J.+Abrams+on+TV%27s+Fringe/ |accessdate=2009-01-08 |quote=I feel like there's a certain thing that you can't really hold onto, which is kind of the kitschy quality. That must go if it's going to be something that you believe is real. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901012953/http://suicidegirls.com/interviews/J.J.%2BAbrams%2Bon%2BTV%27s%2BFringe/ |archivedate=2013-09-01 }}</ref>道具师罗素·博比特（{{small|Russell Bobbitt}}）与[[诺基亚|诺基亚]]进行了合作，对原来的通讯器进行了改造，并制作出了一只价值五万美元的原型。电影中另一个被改造的道具是{{link-en|三录仪|tricorder}}。博比特把原来的道具带到了现场，但演员们都觉得它太过庞大，在拍摄动作场景时很难携带；因此，技术顾问道格·布罗迪（{{small|Doug Brody}}）重新设计了体积缩小版的三录仪。<ref>{{cite news|author=Vic Holtreman|title=Exclusive Interview With The Man Behind Star Trek’s Props|publisher=Screen Rant|date=2009-03-24|url=http://screenrant.com/star-trek-exclusive-interview-man-props-vic-6283/|accessdate=2009-03-24|archive-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927032359/http://screenrant.com/star-trek-exclusive-interview-man-props-vic-6283/|dead-url=no}}</ref>至于相位枪，新的设计给它加上了弹簧触发的圆筒，旋转圆筒待其发出红光后，可以从“击晕档”调成“击毙档”。<ref name=new />此外，拍片场地上还用到了一辆{{link-en|阿帕特拉2系列|Aptera 2 Series|阿帕特拉1型}}（{{small|Aptera Typ-1}}）原型车。<ref>{{cite news|author=Eric Vespe|title=Why do these shots from the filming of "Corporate Headquarters" look suspiciously like the Starfleet Academy?|publisher=Ain't It Cool News|date=2008-03-18|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/36031|accessdate=2008-09-25|archive-date=2008-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206043030/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/36031|dead-url=no}}</ref>

