== 发行 ==
2008年2月，派拉蒙宣布他们将把《星际迷航》的公映日从2008年12月25日推迟至2009年5月8日。制片商觉得在夏季发行将比冬季吸引更多的观众。而实际上，电影的制片工作也直到2008年底才完成。<ref name="TrekDelayTo2009Summer">{{cite news|agency=Associated Press |title='Trek' Boldly Goes to Summer 2009 |work=Starpulse.com |date=2008-02-15 |url=http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2008/02/15/star_trek_boldly_goes_to_summer_2009_in_ |accessdate=2008-09-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331065948/http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2008/02/15/star_trek_boldly_goes_to_summer_2009_in_ |archivedate=2012-03-31 }}</ref>在派拉蒙高层访问了片场并观看了{{link-en|样片|dailies}}后，他们意识到这部电影有着吸引更广泛受众的潜力，因此他们改变了原来的决定。尽管制片人们希望将圣诞节定为公映日，但戴蒙·林德洛夫也承认说，公映延期将让他们有更充足的时间来完善电影的视觉特效。<ref name="wider">{{cite news | author = Anthony Pascale | title = Exclusive Interview: Damon Lindelof On New Release Date and Trek Appealing To Wider Audience | work = TrekMovie | date = 2008-03-01 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/03/01/exclusive-interview-damon-lindelof-on-new-release-date-and-trek-appealing-to-wider-audience/ | accessdate = 2008-03-03 | archive-date = 2013-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130526105025/http://trekmovie.com/2008/03/01/exclusive-interview-damon-lindelof-on-new-release-date-and-trek-appealing-to-wider-audience/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>2008年底制片完成后，离电影的正式发行还有几个月的时间。在此期间，为了写作出电影的小说，{{link-en|艾伦·迪安·福斯特|Alan Dean Foster}}被允许观看了整部电影；不过，他的[[星际迷航_(小说)|小说]]中包含有在最终剪辑里被去掉的情节。<ref>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=Alan Dean Foster Writing Star Trek Movie Adaptation|publisher=|date=2009-02-12|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/12/alan-dean-foster-writing-star-trek-movie-adaptation/|accessdate=2009-02-12|archive-date=2009-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215103909/http://trekmovie.com/2009/02/12/alan-dean-foster-writing-star-trek-movie-adaptation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，电影的有声读物是昆图讲述的。<ref>{{cite news|author=Anthony Pascale|title=ST09 Tidbits (Spocks Edition): Nimoy Supports Vulcans [UPDATED] + Quinto Reads Audiobook & Appears in 