009-06-02|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308121857/https://trekmovie.com/2008/11/19/details-on-first-two-waves-of-playmates-star-trek-movie-toys-neros-ship-name-revealed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>首波玩具包括3.75英寸、6英寸与12英寸的动作玩偶，进取号的模型，道具玩具以及玩具组。要搭造完整的舰桥，玩家需购买足够多的3.75英寸玩偶，椅子和控制台都会随玩偶附带，可以用这些物品组成带有柯克座椅、主控制台以及大屏幕的舰桥模型。<ref>{{cite news|author=John Tenuto|title=Exclusive Details On Playmates Full Line Of Star Trek Movie Toys + Hi Res Images|publisher=|date=2009-01-23|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/01/23/details-and-images-on-playmates-full-line-of-star-trek-movie-toys/|accessdate=2009-01-24|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307193836/https://trekmovie.com/2009/01/23/details-and-images-on-playmates-full-line-of-star-trek-movie-toys/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[复刻大师|复刻大师]]（{{small|Master Replicas}}）、<ref>{{cite news | author = John Tenuto | title = Corgi Announces Star Trek Movie License | work = TrekMovie | date = 2008-01-26 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/01/26/corgi-announces-star-trek-movie-license/ | accessdate = 2008-01-28 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308141438/https://trekmovie.com/2008/01/26/corgi-announces-star-trek-movie-license/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[美泰|美泰]]、[[孩之宝|孩之宝]]以及[[Fundex_Games|Fundex Games]]则会销售相关的游戏产品来宣传电影：包括[[大富翁|大富翁]]、[[UNO|UNO]]、[[Scrabble|Scrabble]]、[[魔术8球|魔术8球]]、[[风火轮_(车模)|风火轮车模]]、{{link-en|Tyco玩具|Tyco Toys|Tyco R/C赛车}}、{{link-en|20Q|20Q|20Q读心机}}、{{link-en|Scene It?|Scene It?}}问答以及[[芭比娃娃|芭比娃娃]]。有一部分游戏产品是基于老版《星际旅行》制作的。<ref name=licenses /><ref>{{cite news|author=John Tenuto|title=Star Trek Hot Wheels Coming in May|publisher=|date=2009-01-19|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/01/19/star-trek-hot-wheels-coming-in-may/|accessdate=2009-01-19|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307231056/https://trekmovie.com/2009/01/19/star-trek-hot-wheels-coming-in-may/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，CBS还创作了一系列基于《星际旅行》的漫画，并将之命名为“Quogs”。<ref>{{