电影的主要演员们均已签约出演后两部续集。<ref>{{cite news | author = Pascale, Anthony | title = Paramount Already Thinking About Sequel To Abrams Star Trek | publisher = TrekMovie | date = 2008-04-06 | url = http://trekmovie.com/2008/06/04/paramount-already-thinking-about-sequel-to-abrams-star-trek/ | accessdate = 2008-06-05 | archive-date = 2011-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111025042325/http://trekmovie.com/2008/06/04/paramount-already-thinking-about-sequel-to-abrams-star-trek/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>[[罗伯托·奥利奇|罗伯托·奥利奇]]、[[亚历克斯·库兹曼|亚历克斯·库兹曼]]与[[戴蒙·林德洛夫|戴蒙·林德洛夫]]于2009年3月就开始撰写续集的剧本，有望在2009年12月时完成剧本，并在制片完成后于2011年中期上映。[[J·J·艾布拉姆斯|J·J·艾布拉姆斯]]与[[布赖恩·伯克|布赖恩·伯克]]将参与制片，但艾布拉姆斯尚未再次签约出任导演。<ref>{{cite news|author=Siegel, Tatiana|title='Star Trek' sequel on track|work=[[剧艺报|剧艺报]]|date=2009-03-30|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118001885.html|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-date=2011-02-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5wWgPKtJk?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118001885.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>当谈到在《星际旅行》中确立的[[平行世界_(虚构作品)|另一个现实]]时<ref name= "mtvalt1">Larry Carroll [http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1611063/20090511/story.jhtml 'Star Trek' Sequel Will Deal With 'Unpredictable Future'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1611063/20090511/story.jhtml |date=20091227080806 }}</ref>，艾布拉姆斯说到，不接受[[威廉·夏特纳|威廉·夏特纳]]复演[[詹姆斯·T·柯克|詹姆斯·T·柯克]]或重塑[[可汗·努尼恩·辛格|可汗·努尼恩·辛格]]的观念是“愚蠢的”。<ref>原文：“whether it's William Shatner or Khan ... it would be ridiculous to not be open to those ideas.”</ref>“现在我们有着一条独立的时间线，可以使用过去的任何元素——或者通过创造崭新的内容——来创作可能的故事情节”，<ref>原文：“The idea, now that we are in an independent timeline, allows us to use any of the ingredients from the past — or come up with brand-new ones — to make potential stories”．</ref>他这样说到。<ref name="mtvalt2">{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|title='Star Trek' Director Open To Sequel With William Shatner Or Khan|work=[[MTV|MTV]]|date=2009-05-15|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1611523/story.jhtml|accessdate=2009-05-16|archive-date=2009-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091207191237/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1611523/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>奥利奇和库兹曼解释了续集的二难选择：是在续集中让船员们再与另一名反面角色战斗，还是让其具有“探索型的科幻情节，让未知事物与大自然本身由于某种原因而成为敌手”。<ref>原文：“[A] exploration sci-fi plot where the unknown and nature itself is somehow an adversary”．</ref>对于重塑可汗的想法，奥利奇反问说：“为甚么要这么选择？”<ref>原文：“why take the chance?”</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Orci & Kurtzman Talk Star Trek Sequel (and the one after that too)|work=TrekMovie|date=2009-06-20|url=http://trekmovie.com/2009/06/20/orci-kurtzman-talk-star-trek-sequel-and-the-one-after-that-too/|accessdate=2009-06-21|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126134441/https://trekmovie.com/2009/06/20/orci-kurtzman-talk-star-trek-sequel-and-the-one-after-that-too/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

